{"tid":36710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保衛香港運動力撐CY：永遠愛您","createTime":"2016-12-13T01:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T12:38:57.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48e2099528d48a454c7dfc49c71b476de2c6120a","tid":36710,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161213/large/1481592055_40fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161213%2Flarge%2F1481592055_40fa.jpg&h=52c0abf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「珍惜群組」和「保衛香港運動」共20多人，今早在梁振英宣佈不連任特首後首次行會前，在特首辦門外拉起「感謝特首過去辛勞和貢獻永遠愛您」橫額，又舉起「CY我撐你」、「疾風知勁草，板蕩識忠臣」等標語，準備到行會示威區見梁振英，不少人戴上太陽眼鏡。「收工男」傅振中更率先入場，佔據示威區有利位置。"},{"pid":"bf879821bac97f21217d72bc2a7b79370d0f02f9","tid":36710,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:31:56.000Z","msg":"冇左隻狗主人<br />\n呢班撚樣失業喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccf10b48d991d3355d8244f0b5576c9fcb31cb1","tid":36710,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自導自演"},{"pid":"3dcb972c5554952eca622e127b619fe43ad65a8f","tid":36710,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:32:49.000Z","msg":"得20人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個啲咩幫港發聲 愛港力 做咩唔叫多啲人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68338d4d5667267295e495da11ea5bc5be6e11dd","tid":36710,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T01:34:34.000Z","msg":"冇錢收冇人愛"},{"pid":"7ec1a02157510166d3df3e0865c0bd39cadbfa8d","tid":36710,"uid":64496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor